Pimme is a basic Personal Information Manager written in Python.  It
stores data in encrypted format in a file and supports copying a value
to the clipboard automatically.

Installation
-----------------
Use 
$ ./setup.sh install
to install.  It uses ~/lib/python/ and ~/bin directories for the files.
Uninstall with
$ ./setup.sh uninstall

Look in ~/.pimme.conf for available settings.
